{"tid":2081390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普簽署行政命令要求起訴破壞紀念碑及銅像的人士","createTime":"2020-06-27T07:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T07:57:57.000Z","uid":166360,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b48d86cadc4e84379e2763321001eac6d8297fbf","tid":2081390,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:42:53.000Z","msg":"特朗普簽署行政命令要求起訴破壞紀念碑及銅像的人士<br />\n2020-06-27 HKT 14:01<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普在社交網站表示，他已經簽署行政命令，授權執法人員保護紀念碑及銅像，有關命令將要求檢察當局，起訴破壞或塗鴉紀念碑及銅像的人士，認為有關行為是故意損毀聯邦財產，根據現行法例，涉案人士最高可被判處10年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534400-20200627.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534400-20200627.htm&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFvS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=5955b6d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534400-20200627.htm&h=e97b9331\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534400-20200627.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">破壞歷史文物非常可惡，支持美國當局嚴正執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8931e31498c486c782cfa55b386b29f44c0f6d95","tid":2081390,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:55:04.000Z","msg":"香港無人會支持破壞文物<br />\n除非係共產主義晚垃圾雕像"},{"pid":"2d2f7ea4af6041dd50489448bed9affa51a3afab","tid":2081390,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:56:53.000Z","msg":"BLM 根本俾人騎劫左<br />\n越玩越大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be73fe65927a22e9e73ae0fbd8e34af70730b1b0","tid":2081390,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T07:57:57.000Z","msg":"ho ball"}]}